      <title>里约热内卢花费18亿美元扩大皮尔巴拉铁矿石枢纽</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/rio-tinto-to-spend-1-8-billion-to-expand-pilbara-iron-ore-hub</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里约热内卢集团（Rio Tinto Group）将花费18亿美元在西澳大利亚州皮尔巴拉（Pilbara）地区扩大其布罗克人铁矿石枢纽，随着较老的矿山的耗尽，寻求维持足够的炼钢材料生产水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-06/rio-tinto-to-spend-1-8-billion-to-expand-pilbara-iron-ore-hub</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Mar 2025 04:28:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
